<div><div><h2>IL&FS row: Arun Jaitley hits out at Rahul Gandhi, says section of Congress urged him to enable investments in it</h2></div><div>calling out congress’ doublespeak finance minister on monday said while a section of the party leadership had been urging him to enable investments in il&fs its chief rahul gandhi was calling it a “scam”. calling congress a “national saboteur” jaitley also made public a letter written by congress leader and former union minister kv thomas to him on ways to bail out the debt-laden company which has a long-term liability of around rs 91000 crore.</div></div>